svg.title: W3C Community Groups Logo
svg.desc: This is a symbol of unity and collaboration with diversity. Four stylized human figures in a circle, with arms reaching out to one another, heads pointed outward, bodies tapering in toward the center of the circle. The figures are different colors (light blue, pale green, red, and orange), and different sizes. This image links back to the W3C Community Groups site.
